         <desc>
            <persName ref="https://usaybia.net/person/1401"></persName>
            <placeName ref="https://usaybia.net/place/121">Cairo</placeName>
            <choice>
               <reg>
                  <date when"1243" calendar="#julian">1243</date>
               </reg>
               <orig>
                  <date when="632" calendar="#hijri">632</date>
               </orig>
            </choice>
            <listRelation>
               <relation type="person" ref="http://syriaca.org/keyword/student-of" active="https://usaybia.net/person/1401" passive="https://usaybia.net/person/926"></relation><!-- The other way around!-->
               Ibn Abī Uṣaybiʿah met Afḍal al-Dīn al-Khūnajī in Cairo and studied under him a part of <persname ref="https://usaybia.net/person/1125">al-Raʾīs Ibn Sīnā</persname>'s Kitāb al-Qānūn. 
            </listRelation>
         </desc>
      </event>
   </listEvent>
   <bibl type="urn">
      <ptr target="urn:cts:arabicLit:0668IbnAbiUsaibia.Tabaqatalatibba.lhom-ed-ara1:14.48"></ptr>
